        <stages>
            <li>
                <label>Omega Pariah</label>
                <description>I am nothing, yet I am everything they fear. The warp crumbles in my presence, its whispers silenced, its corruption halted. I am the void, the end of the unnatural, and the last hope against the darkness.</description>
